<p>
<note n="0652003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0652003">光明皇后願文【聖】</note>
<note n="0652004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0652004">逆＝是【聖】</note>
<note n="0652005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0652005">已＝無【宮】</note>
<note n="0653001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0653001">利＋（汝）【明】</note>
<note n="0653002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0653002">及＝者【三】</note>
<note n="0653003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0653003">住＝非【宮】</note>
